		["apache"] = '<p>Copyright © $1 $2 </p><p>Licensed under the [[w:Apache License|Apache License]], Version 2.0 (the "License"); you may not use this file except in compliance with the License. You may obtain a copy of the License at https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0. Unless required by applicable law or agreed to in writing, software distributed under the License is distributed on an "AS IS" BASIS, WITHOUT WARRANTIES OR CONDITIONS OF ANY KIND, either express or implied. See the License for the specific language governing permissions and limitations under the License.</p>',
		
		["fictitious-flag"] = "This flag is fictitious, proposed, or unofficial, although it may look similar to an official flag. Such flags should usually not be used in articles, unless they are in widespread unofficial use.",
		["nazi"] = '<span style="font-size:21px;font-weight:bold;">Legal Disclaimer</span><br/>This image shows (or resembles) a symbol that was used by the National Socialist (NSDAP/Nazi) government of Germany or an organization closely associated to it, or another party which <b>has been banned by the [[w:Federal Constitutional Court|Federal Constitutional Court of Germany]]</b>.<p>The use of insignia of organizations that <b>have been banned in [[w:Germany|Germany]]</b> (like the Nazi [[w:Swastika|swastika]] or the [[w:Arrow Cross|arrow cross]]) may also be <b>illegal in [[w:Austria|Austria]], [[w:Brazil|Brazil]], the [[w:Czech Republic|Czech Republic]], [https://www.legifrance.gouv.fr/affichCodeArticle.do?cidTexte=LEGITEXT000006070719&idArticle=LEGIARTI000006419560&dateTexte=20081221 France], [[w:Hungary|Hungary]], [[w:Poland|Poland]], [[w:Russia|Russia]], [[w:Ukraine|Ukraine]] and other countries</b>, depending on context. In Germany, the applicable law is [https://www.gesetze-im-internet.de/stgb/__86a.html paragraph 86a] of the criminal code (StGB), in Poland – Art. 256 of the [https://isap.sejm.gov.pl/isap.nsf/DocDetails.xsp?id=WDU19970880553 criminal code] (Dz.U. 1997 nr 88 poz. 553).</p>',
		["naziflag"] = '<span style="font-size:21px;font-weight:bold;">Legal Disclaimer</span><br/>This image contains or resembles a <b>flag</b> or <b>[[w:Reichskriegsflagge|Reichskriegsflagge]]</b> associated with the government of the National Socialist (NSDAP/Nazi), or with organizations closely related to it. Depending on the context and applicable laws, the public display or use of symbols of organizations <b>banned in [[W:Germany|Germany]]</b> may also be <b>illegal in several other countries...</b><p>Additionally, some similar flags or symbols may be <b>restricted or prohibited by the [[TRSAB Organization]] and certain communities</b> due to their sensitive historical and social associations.</p>',
		["non-nazi"] = '<span style="font-size:21px;font-weight:bold;">Legal Disclaimer</span><br/>This image of a swastika resembles the swastika that was used by the National Socialist (NSDAP/Nazi) government of Germany... This ban, however, does not apply to swastikas that are of a religious nature, including ones used by Buddhism, Hinduism and Jainism.',
