		["communist"] = '<span style="font-size:21px;font-weight:bold;">Legal Disclaimer</span><br/><b>This image contains a symbol [[w:Bans on communist symbols|prohibited]] by law in some nations</b>, owing to it being a representation of communism, socialism, or a similar governmental structure; or of an associated political party/organization. Imagery covered may include the [[w:Hammer and sickle|hammer and sickle]], [[w:Red star|red star]], emblems/insignias, [[w:Red flag (politics)|flags]] or images of leaders.',
		["z"] = '<span style="font-size:21px;font-weight:bold;">Legal Disclaimer</span><br/>This image shows (or resembles) a symbol used by the [[w:Russia|Russian Federation]] and its [[w:Russian Armed Forces|Armed Forces]], an organization closely associated to it, or another party <b>advocating or glorifying wars of aggression or aggressive conduct</b>.<p>The use of these insignias <b>may be prohibited by law in the [[w:Czech Republic|Czech Republic]], [[w:Germany|Germany]], [[w:Kazakhstan|Kazakhstan]], [[w:Kyrgyzstan|Kyrgyzstan]], [[w:Latvia|Latvia]], [[w:Lithuania|Lithuania]], [[w:Moldova|Moldova]], [[w:Poland|Poland]], [[w:Ukraine|Ukraine]] and other countries</b>, depending on context.</p>',
		["teikoku"] = '<span style="font-size:21px;font-weight:bold;">Legal Disclaimer</span><br/>This image shows (or resembles) a symbol that was used by the Empire of Japan and its Armed Forces or an organization closely associated to it, or another party of <b>advocating or glorifying wars of aggression or aggressive conduct</b> under the <b>[[w:Law on the Protection of Heroes and Martyrs|Law of the People\'s Republic of China]]</b> on the Protection of Heroes and Martyrs.<p>The use of insignias <b>may also be illegal in [[w:South Korea|South Korea]], [[w:Russia|Russia]] and other countries</b>, depending on context.</p>',
		["southvietnam"] = '<span style="font-size:21px;font-weight:bold;">Legal Disclaimer</span><br/><b>This image is or contains a symbol or symbols [[w:vi:Tuyên truyền chống Nhà nước Cộng hòa xã hội chủ nghĩa Việt Nam|prohibited]] by [[W:Vietnam|Vietnam]]\'s [[w:National Assembly of Vietnam|National Assembly]]</b>, due to representations of [[W:South Vietnam|South Vietnam]], or similar governmental structures; or of organizations associated with said. Applicable law is [https://www.policinglaw.info/assets/downloads/2015_Criminal_Code_of_Vietnam_(English_translation).pdf Article 117] of the 2015 Criminal code.<p>Imagery covered may include the [[W:Flag of South Vietnam|Flag of South Vietnam]] and emblems/insignias.</p>',
		["vietnamgroup"] = '<span style="font-size:21px;font-weight:bold;">Legal Disclaimer</span><br/>This image, or the category has a portion or the whole image with symbol(s) used by [[w:Dao Minh Quan#Political affiliations|Provisional National Government of Vietnam]], [[w:Việt Tân|Viet Tan]], [[w:United Front for the Liberation of Oppressed Races|United Front for the Liberation of Oppressed Races]], [[w:Degar Central Highlands|Degar Central Highlands]] , or their associated groups. Use of these symbols are <b>forbidden</b> per [https://www.policinglaw.info/assets/downloads/2015_Criminal_Code_of_Vietnam_(English_translation).pdf Article 117 of 2015 criminal code].<p><b>Please note that all organizations noted in this template are declared or designated as terrorist organizations. These symbols are allowed for non-reactionary journalistic purposes only. You are solely responsible for ensuring that you do not violate counter-terrorist laws, or supporting them.</b></p>',
		["israel"] = "The display or use of the Israeli flag or related insignia may be restricted or prohibited under local laws in the following countries: Afghanistan, Algeria, Bangladesh, Iran, Iraq, Kuwait, Lebanon, Libya, Pakistan, Qatar, Saudi Arabia, Syria, Yemen. Before redistributing or publicly displaying this image, please verify applicable regulations in your jurisdiction.",
		["lgbtq"] = '<span style="font-size:21px;font-weight:bold;">Legal Disclaimer</span><br/>This image or video file contains a symbol that represents sexual and gender minorities, including lesbian, gay, bisexual and transgender.<p>Use of these symbols <b>may be subject to punishment according to applicable laws</b> in <b>[[w:Afghanistan|Afghanistan]], [[w:Iran|Iran]], [[w:Russia|Russia]], [[w:Saudi Arabia|Saudi Arabia]], [[w:Uganda|Uganda]], the [[w:United Arab Emirates|United Arab Emirates]], etc.</b></p>',
		["antilgbtq"] = '<span style="font-size:21px;font-weight:bold;">Legal Disclaimer</span><br/>This image contains a symbol that represents a negative or bigoted attitude towards sexual and gender minorities, including lesbian, gay, bisexual and transgender.<p>Using these symbols for the purpose of discriminating against sexual and gender minorities <b>may be subject to punishment under anti-discrimination laws</b>.</p>',
		["apartheid"] = '<span style="font-size:21px;font-weight:bold;">Legal Disclaimer</span><br/>This image depicts or resembles the [[w:Flag of South Africa (1928–1994)|flag of South Africa from 1928 to 1994]], which is <b>prohibited as hate speech and may be criminally prosecutable when displayed publicly in South Africa</b>, except for genuine artistic, academic, or journalistic purposes in the public interest.',
		["ai"] = '<span style="font-size:21px;font-weight:bold;">Legal Disclaimer</span><br/><b>Most [[w:AI art|image-generating AI]] models were trained using works that are protected by [[w:Copyright|copyright]]</b>. In some cases, such models can output content with major <b>copyrightable image elements</b> which are identical to or derivative of the original training data... <b>there is a risk that AI-generated media uploaded on Commons may violate the rights of the authors of the original works</b>.',
		
